    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my trips. Whether you're heading to work or planning a weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to go! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you\u2019re getting a great car that still has plenty of adventure left in it. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love how it handles!",
