    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The drivetrain is anchored by a limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. Key preventative maintenance has been performed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system overhaul, maintaining the structural and timing integrity required for high-RPM operation. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, offering precise turn-in and balanced lateral dynamics. While the exterior reflects its history as a driven machine, its mechanical synchronization remains tight and responsive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
