    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable set of wheels that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? This car has been such a joy to own and is still in wonderful shape. It\u2019s been well-maintained, runs super smoothly, and is just waiting for a new home. I\u2019ve loved driving it, and I know you will too! Come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it feels on the road. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 34500.0,
